{
  "stem": "22047.4",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "By the time we left, 'heil Hitler' was erased, and there was a rainbow on it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We painted rainbows on everything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Wherever we'd go, there'd be a rainbow when we left.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "There must have been 1,000 rainbows across Alsace-Lorraine and-- and into Germany and across Germany.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And so we pushed on then after our fight in Wurzburg.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "We lost, oh, three or four people in Wurzburg, because we were-- that was-- that was pretty heavy combat.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "The next real heavy combat was in Furth-Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We-- our-- my particular company's objective was the airport at Furth.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we had quite a battle there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Although I-- in retrospect, I felt quite sorry for some of the folks we killed.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were-- they were air-- air force cadets.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "We didn't know it at the time, but it turned out that they were air force cadets.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And one of the battalion commanders, or the commander of this unit-- school, I guess it was, at the Furth airport-- was a-- a a colonel, oberst.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "I guess it was oberstleutnant, lieutenant colonel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "We killed him.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And it turned out that he was the commandant of the school, and oh-- [SIGHS] You know, at the one time, here's an enemy.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But they're-- they're cadets.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They're young kids.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And here's that colonel that probably was over age.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he was killed, too.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And-- and you even felt sorry for those folks in the heat of combat.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "But they had weapons.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And so unfortunately, we had to-- had to try to-- try to-- to kill them.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Kill or be killed was the motto in those days.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And then we-- we moved from the airport across the river into Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And we had city fighting then, heavy city fighting.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We fought for two days in Nuremberg.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
